'''Didier Drogba''' waa cayaaryahan u dhashay wadanka [[Xeebta Foolmaroodi|Ivory Coast ]], waxoona hadda u ciyaaraa  kooxda central forward oo ku taal galbeedka [[London]] ee wadanka [[Ingiriiska|England]], waa kaptanka sadexaad ee kooxda Drogba wuxuu ku soo biiray cayaaraha isagoo jira 15 sano, waxoona bilaabay iskuuul ku yaalo magaalo madaxda labaad ee wadanka [[Faransiiska]] [[Marseille]].Wuxuu ku soo biiray marseil sanadki [[2000]]. Kow iyo tobanka ugu horaysa kooxda wuxuu u cayaarayayay mudo dhan 4 sano, isagoo dhashay 95 gool. Sanadii [[2004]]kina waxaa la soo wareegta kooxda  ee [[Chelsea FC|Chelsea]] oo la ciyaare 8 sanado. Hadda wuxu la ciyaara kooxda [[Galatasaray SK]] ee [[Turkiga]].

